<div class="rbox" name="tip">
<div class="rbox-title" name="tip">{tr}Tip{/tr}</div>  
<div class="rbox-data" name="tip">{tr}To learn more about <a class="rbox-link" target="tikihelp" href="http://themes.tikiwiki.org">themes</a>.{/tr}
